      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zedeüra Dehlam/buhs teem Ruh-\nbenza Behrneemi par Wirfneeku\nbuht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks/ un\nwinna Pulki bija tſchetrdefinits\nfeſch tuhkſtoschi un peeztints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un klaht winnu buhs tai\nSihmeana Zilti to Lehgeri ap-\nmest/ un Selunniêlam/ ZuriSa-\ndaja Dehlam/ buhs teem Sih-\nmeana Behrneem par Wirfneeku\nbuht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks/ un\nwinna Pulki bija peeżdefinits\ndewia tuhkſtoschi/ un trihzints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un klaht tai Zilti/ Gads;\nUn Eeliaſawam/ Regueła Deh-\nlam/ buhs teem Gada Behrneem\npar Wirfneeku buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks/ un\nwinna Pulki bija tſchetrdefinits\npeeż tuhkſtoschi/ feſchſints/ un\npeeżdefinits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſi Pulki/ ta Rubbe-\nna Lehgera/bija ſints peeżdefinits\nun ween tuhkſtoschi/ tſchetrtints\nun peeżdefinits/ pehz ſaweeim\nPulkeem/ un teem buhs ohtrâ\nPulkâ zeltees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz to buhs tai Sa-ce-\nſchanas Zelti zeltees/ ar to Lewi-\ntu Lehgeri/starp teem Lehgereem/\nittin ka tee to Lehgeri apinett/ ta\nbuhs teem zeltees/ ikweenam fa-\nwâ Weetâ/ pehz winnu Karro-\ngeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Geiwâima Lehgera\nKarrogam buhs prett Wakkaru\nbuht/ pehz ſaweeim Pulkeem/ un\nEeltsamam/ Amiuda Dehlam/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks/ u\nwinna Pulki bija tſchetrdefinit\ntuhkſtoschi/ un peeztints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un klaht winnu buhs Ma\nnaſſus Zilts/un Gamiliêlam/ Pe-\ndazuxa Dehlam/ buhs teem Ma-\nnaſſus Behrneem par Wirfneek-\nbuht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks/ u\nwinna Pulki bija trihzdefinit\ndiwi tuhkſtoschi/un diwitints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tad buhs Benjamiz-\nZilts; Un Abidanam/ Gideo-\nDehlam/ buhs teem Benjamiz-\nBehrneem par Wirfneeku buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks un\nwinna Pulki bija trihzdefinite\npeeż tuhkſtoschi/ un tſchetrtunts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi Pulki/ta Gewräima\nLehgera bija ſints un aſtoxtuhk-\nſtoschi/ un ſints/ pehz ſaweeim\nPulkeem/ un teem buhs treſchâ\nPulkâ zeltees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tam Karrogam ta Dann-\nLehgera buhs prett Seemeli buht/\npehz ſaweeim Pulkeem/ un Aki-\nſeram/ AmmiSadaja Dehlam-\nbuhs teem Danna Behrneem par\nWirfneeku buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks/ un\nwinna Pulki bija feſchdefinits di-\nwi tuhkſtoschi/ un ſeptintints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un klaht winnu buhs Ah-\nfera Zilts/ un Pagielam/ Okran-\nDehlam/buhs teem Ahsera Behr-\nneem par Wirfneeku buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta paſcha Spehks un\nwinna Pulki bija tſchetrdefinit\n"
    }
  ],
